        public static int javaMajorVersion()
        Gets java major version.

        If java version <= 1.8, return second version number such as 6 for 1.6.x, 8 for 1.8.x. Else return first number such as 9 for 9.0.

        Return -1 if obtain failed.

        返回:
        java major version
